videos.description: The Spartans' Nick Ward leaps over a gate on the baseline by the media.
videos.headline: Michigan States' Ward with an athletic leap

videos.description: Michigan State's Lourawls Nairn Jr. finds Matt McQuaidin the corner who drives it in for a layup.
videos.headline: McQuaid kisses ball off glass for a layup

videos.description: The Spartans' Cassius Winston lobs it up high to Miles Bridges for a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Michigan State's Bridges throws down alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Off the rebound, Nick Ward slams it home for a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Spartans' Ward with a putback jam

videos.description: Jaren Jackson Jr. slams one home after getting dunked on by Indiana player.
videos.headline: Michigan State's Jackson jumps up high for a dunk

videos.description: Miles Bridges drives in for a monster one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Spartans' Bridges shows no mercy to the rim
